3
00:00:10,636 --> 00:00:12,596
MOODY: Long enough for Lexie
to have their wedding planned.

4
00:00:12,888 --> 00:00:15,349
‐ I'm going to Yale.
‐ Congratulations.

5
00:00:15,349 --> 00:00:17,184
‐ She hasn't even applied yet.

6
00:00:17,184 --> 00:00:19,102
‐ Oh, so you want to change
your math class.

7
00:00:19,102 --> 00:00:22,022
