from taking advanced courses.

8
00:00:22,981 --> 00:00:25,734
LEXIE: <i>I think I figured out what</i>
<i>I'm gonna do for my Yale essay.</i>

9
00:00:27,819 --> 00:00:31,281
‐ If you don't stand up for yourself,
who will?

10
00:00:32,491 --> 00:00:35,869
I'd like to help you in your household
if the offer still stands.

11
00:00:35,869 --> 00:00:37,621
‐ Sure.

12
00:00:37,621 --> 00:00:41,416
‐ Hon, look, you're allowed to change
your mind if you don't want her there.

13
00:00:41,667 --> 00:00:45,087
‐ I did lie.
I put down a fake reference.

14
00:00:45,087 --> 00:00:46,713
But I'm not a criminal.

15
00:00:48,173 --> 00:00:49,258
‐ Why don't we have a glass of wine?

16
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:52,219
‐ What's going on with her?

17
00:00:52,219 --> 00:00:54,054
BEBE: <i>I had a daughter.</i>

18
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:55,180
‐ What was her name?

19
00:00:56,473 --> 00:00:57,349
