23
00:01:33,886 --> 00:01:36,346
[speaking Mandarin]

24
00:01:52,988 --> 00:01:55,490
[baby crying]

25
00:01:57,993 --> 00:01:59,828
[speaking indistinctly in Mandarin]

26
00:01:59,828 --> 00:02:01,246
[coins jingling]

27
00:02:06,084 --> 00:02:07,544
‐ You're 70 cents short.

28
00:02:07,544 --> 00:02:10,547
‐ Please, she not eat for days.
I not eat for week.

29
00:02:10,547 --> 00:02:12,758
‐ Then try breastfeeding.
It's free.

30
00:02:13,175 --> 00:02:15,928
‐ Please.
‐ Get the fuck out of my store!

31
